item.dc:creator: @w-e_s-l_e-y w-e_s-l_e-y@hotmail.com
item.description:
@w-e_s-l_e-y wrote:

Open up the folder of your client (not your source!)
Go into the client.java file and search for the client name and change it into yours.

To change the ip look for something like: server or ip or something like that and change it into yours, I hope you understand it.

Take a look at the tutorial section.
